snippet.title: Infinity Blaster - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2090640/Infinity_Blaster/

In Infinity Blaster you blast through space, defeat challenging enemies and upgrade your weapons! Compete on the global leaderboard, survive an infinite loop of increasingly difficult foes, and unlock 98 achievements. Can you prove yourself as the ultimate space adventurer
